Current members
* Chad Kroeger – lead vocals, lead guitar 
* Ryan Peake – rhythm guitar, backing vocals , keyboards 
* Mike Kroeger – bass 
* Daniel Adair – drums, percussion, backing vocals 

Former members
* Brandon Kroeger – drums 
* Mitch Guindon – drums 
* Ryan Vikedal – drums, percussion 

